-- MOVES-Rothschild names Kevin Gardiner as global investment strategist
-- 
-- Tue Jul 01, 2014 12:25PM EDT
-- None



July 1 (Reuters) - Financial advisory services provider Rothschild [ROT.UL] appointed Kevin Gardiner as global investment strategist in its wealth management unit.

Gardiner, who will join on August 18, will play a prominent role in the global investment committee, the company said.